40275741867025900.Text: Exotic products of commercial value on Vvardenfell include the following: bonemeal, corprus weepings, Daedra skin, Daedra's heart, ectoplasm, fire salts, frost salts, Ghoul heart, gravedust, raw ebony, raw glass, Scamp skin, Vampire dust, and void salts.
